        "body": "Thanks for the prompt response. \n\nLooking at [chrome.history API](https://developer.chrome.com/extensions/history) the `VisitItem` object has the property `referringVisitId` which is \"The visit ID of the referrer.\". Coupling this with [TransitionType](https://developer.chrome.com/extensions/history#type-TransitionType) wouldn't it be possible to get info on the parent page. \n"
